            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Rainerius">[Ragi]nerius</name></persName> filio
                        quondam item <persName><name ref="Rainerius">Ragineri</name></persName>
                        concede in livello a <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/226"
                            >Atio</persName>, <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti
                            Bartholomei</orgName> posito in <rs key="#Mountains">pogio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Mountains #Mills #Carbonaria #Cisterns/pits #Canals"
                            ref="#places/293">Sancti Frudiani</placeName><placeName
                            ref="#places/281">Sestinge</placeName>, (…) idest integra meam
                        porc(ionem) de <rs key="#Mountains">pogio</rs> Sancti Frudiani, prope
                        Sestinge, coheret a predicto pogio, sicuti currit <rs key="#Canals"
                            >gora</rs> de <rs key="#Mills">molino</rs> et de fini
                            <placeName>Furcula</placeName> et sicuti est circundato a <rs
                            key="#Carbonaria">carbonagia</rs> et prope <placeName>Gricanico de
                            Grattadosso</placeName> et de fini via publica et de fini
                            <placeName>Casallia</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions" ref="#juridical_persons/126"
                            >Sancti Bartholomei</orgName> et [tenet] caput in canpo de
                                <placeName><rs key="#Cisterns/pits">Piscina</rs> Sacra</placeName>
                        et de fini predicta gora a sicuti apedovata fuit per per <persName><name
                                ref="Rotioctus">Rozotto</name></persName> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Bonfilius">Bonifilii</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Bandulus de Palagia">Bandulo</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Palagia</placeName>, con tutte le sue dipendenze; la quota
                        spettante a Ranieri est sextam pars sicut circumdata est (…) plano et pogio
                        in integrum. L’abate si impegna a versare a Ranieri e ai suoi eredi per omne
                        mense agusti ficto denarii Lucensis solidos duobus (…) dato ipso ficto et
                        consignato a predictus Raginerius vel eius heredibus vel ad eorum missos si
                        recipere voluerit infra <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes"><placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/355"
                                >Giuncalico</placeName></geogName>; Ranieri e i suoi eredi a
                        difendere i diritti del monastero aut cui pars suprascripto monasterio
                        dederint aut concesserint secundum legem ab omni homine; penam argenti
                        libras viginti. Se non rispetteranno i suddetti impegni, entrambe le parti
                        promettono di versare la pena di 20 libbre d’argento. Actum Giuncalico de
                            <rs key="#Dioecesis">episcopato</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Dioecesis" ref="#estates/154">Rosolense</geogName>. Testi:
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rotiolinus"
                            >Rozulini</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name ref="Rotius"
                                >Rozi</name></persName>; <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrando</name></persName> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Sclavus">Sclavi</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Einrici</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodelandus">Rolando</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Rusticus">Rustici</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodelandus">Rolando</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Anselmus">Anselmi</name></persName>. Scrive:
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Hugo"
                            >Ugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> sacri
                        palatii.</ab>
                        </div>
